
<div class="reviewbg">

        <div style="display: flex;flex-direction: row;justify-content: center;">
            <div id="commentfonts">
                <h1 id="commenthead">COMMENTS</h1>
                <p>Your reviews help us improve, be sure to leave one out.</p>
                <p><a href="/reviews/new" id="newtaglink">Drop a Comment!</a></p>
